    "It is a measure of the model's ability to retrieve positive examples.",
    "The precision-recall curve plots the precision against the recall for different threshold values.",
    "The AUC-PR is computed as the area under the precision-recall curve.",
    "After the fine-tuning and the definition of the performance measures, the model can be saved and is ready to use in the task defined.",
